,What differentiates Error 19-14 from Error 19-15 in terms of cause?,Error 19-14 is due to loading a dynamic software module, while Error 19-15 is due to initialization of protected memory.","The former involves a dynamic software module loading error, the latter a protected memory initialization issue.","19-14 stems from a software module load error, whereas 19-15 comes from protected memory init failure.",Dynamic software module loading causes 19-14; protected memory initialization causes 19-15.,"19-14's cause is dynamic module load failure, 19-15's is memory initialization error."
